snippet: Odyssey Sims scored a career-high 48 points and set a Baylor record for career 3-pointers in the seventh-ranked Bears' 78-62 victory over West Virginia on Wednesday night....

headline.print_headline: Sims Has 48 Points, Baylor Women Top W. Virginia
headline.main: Sims Has 48 Points, Baylor Women Top W. Virginia

lead_paragraph: Odyssey Sims scored a career-high 48 points and set a Baylor record for career 3-pointers in the seventh-ranked Bears' 78-62 victory over West Virginia on Wednesday night.
